G 討論區<br />\n<br />\n(請廣傳)立法會初選與三不投聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1967776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1967776</a><br />\n<br />\n（緊急）「攬炒藝術家」：聯署要人！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1966811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1966811</a><br />\n<br />\n【堅。找數真漢子】呢個聯署過一百萬簽名我裸跑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1955200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1955200</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉就到啦，我哋有咩可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1968274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1968274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad0587c7cd951f1f1520edd4e46ef44da2f8f800","tid":1991751,"uid":307502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2244f2cd1518947a05317a40ba8915746207a033","tid":1991751,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d926a1cb16ac5316bbfb1f0107bfe382a7fef62d","tid":1991751,"uid":1188,"like":14,"dislike":53,"score":-39,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"有心跳一早跳咗啦<br />\n都唔知駁乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"做乜把口咁臭"},{"pid":"c9a302fce62f3342163d40d6e16d7a2f4dde93de","tid":1991751,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24d6a626b96717f1df812e8fd6f02127d48108e4","tid":1991751,"uid":35315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:34:15.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1faf4e583a9fb6c05bf4271dbf4bb59ebfb92074","tid":1991751,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92aa1264700e56bb077eb75386c37a67dac73b2","tid":1991751,"uid":255884,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea8cffff0ff8a0f5ac6b614c997c67a3e11b5a5f","tid":1991751,"uid":224657,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"b42e61e61102bd8b48f601b1ba1963a0cade8d04","tid":1